---
// src/components/Hero.astro
---

<section class="hero">
  <!-- Profile photo -->
  <div class="hero__photo-wrap">
    <div class="hero__photo">
      <img src="/images/Hero.png" alt="Nass Riviera" />
    </div>
    <div class="hero__badge">
      <span>VibeCoder</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Name -->
  <h1 class="hero__name">
    NASS <br />
    <span class="hero__name-gradient">RIVIERA</span>
  </h1>

  <!-- Tagline -->
  <p class="hero__tagline">
    Entrepreneur & Investisseur depuis 2017, c'est en 2026 que je prends la décision <strong>radicale</strong> d'arrêter les cryptomonnaies suite à un dégoût viscéral. Je partage en toute humilité la reconstruction d'un écosystème grâce au VibeCoding.
  </p>
</section>

<style>
  .hero {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
    padding: var(--space-2xl) var(--space-lg) var(--space-xl);
  }

  /* Photo */
  .hero__photo-wrap {
    position: relative;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2xl);
  }

  .hero__photo {
    width: 12rem;
    height: 12rem;
    border-radius: var(--radius-full);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .hero__photo img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    border-radius: var(--radius-full);
    transition: filter 0.7s ease;
    transform: scale(1.05);
  }

  .hero__photo:hover img {
    filter: grayscale(0%);
  }

  .hero__badge {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -1rem;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    white-space: nowrap;
    padding: 0.25rem 1rem;
    border-radius: var(--radius-full);
    background: rgba(19, 19, 19, 0.6);
    backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .hero__badge span {
    font-family: var(--font-label);
    font-size: 0.625rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-cyan);
  }

  /* Name */
  .hero__name {
    font-family: var(--font-headline);
    font-size: clamp(3rem, 12vw, 5rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    line-height: 0.95;
    color: white;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .hero__name-gradient {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00D4FF 0%, #A8E8FF 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }

  /* Tagline */
  .hero__tagline {
    max-width: 20rem;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.7;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
  }


  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .hero__name {
      font-size: 5rem;
    }
  }
</style>
